fields.name: Yellowstone Classic
fields.description: Your best bet for style and elegance. The variety of colors and finishes combined with the organic texture of the high-quality leather strap make Yellowstone Leather a masculine collection which oozes personality.

fields.name: Loews LQ1.201
fields.description: The Loews Chronograph watch by Nezumi is inspired by several 1960s chronographs and has a vintage vibe with classic color schemes. It’s powered by a mechanical-quartz movement made by Seiko and features two sub-dials – 24-hour and 60-minute counter – and a double-domed genuine sapphire crystal with anti-reflective coating on the inside.

fields.name: PR 100 Chronograph
fields.description: True to its name, the Tissot PR 100 is Precise and Robust and a hugely popular family within the Tissot range. These new pieces have been launched to give a more modern look in keeping with the time yet still combining traditional watch design using quality materials and the Swiss reliability of the movement.

fields.name: Smart Watch Function F5
fields.description: The F5 model of the Kuura Function smartwatches series is a smart watch equipped with a stylish design and a silicone wristband. The smartwatch can monitors and observes your body's activity such as sleep, movement and health. The device is equipped with a large 1.3 ”IPS Multi-touch color display and a powerful 200mAh battery. You can connect the watch directly to your smartphone, so you can conveniently receive notifications on your smartwatch. In addition, the smartwatch transfers collected data to the smartwatch's own application, where you can easily access the collected data.

fields.name: Submariner Date
fields.description: It features a unidirectional rotatable bezel with Cerachrom insert and solid-link Oyster bracelet. The latest generation Submariner and Submariner Date remain faithful to the original model launched in 1953. In watchmaking, the Submariner represented a historic turning point; it set the standard for divers’ watches.

fields.name: Mechanical Classic
fields.description: The watch’s rounded boxed glass elegantly frames the curved antique silver bombe dial, set in a beautiful stainless steel silver case. An attractive see-through case back enhances the refined aesthetic.

fields.name: Radiomir Firenze
fields.description:
The Radiomir is the first watch designed by Officine Panerai as a prototype in 1936 at the request of the Royal Italian Navy, which wanted to be supplied with “a special luminous watch for divers”.
Diameter 45 mm, AISI 316L Polished Steel with removable wire loop strap attachments (patented).

fields.name: Luminor Marina
fields.description: Automatic mechanical, P.9010 calibre, executed entirely by Panerai, 13¾ lignes, 6.0 mm thick, 31 jewels, Glucydur® balance, 28,800 alternations/hour. Incabloc® anti-shock device. Power reserve 3 days, two barrels. 200 components

fields.name: Bronson Chronograph Luggage
fields.description:
A casual robust watch for the daily routine.
Strap Width: 24MM
Battery Type: SR920SW

fields.name: Prospex LX Line
fields.description:
The Seiko Prospex LX line. The true spirit of Seiko.
Prospex LX. At the pinnacle of sport, on land, at sea and in the sky.

fields.name: Machine Three-Hand Date
fields.description:
Simple by fashion but always reliable.
Case Material: Stainless Steel
Water Resistance: 5 ATM - Battery Type: SR621SW

fields.name: Smart Watch Series 6
fields.description: Silver Stainless Steel Case with Milanese Loop - The stainless steel case is durable and polished to a shiny, mirror-like finish. The Milanese Loop is made from a smooth stainless steel mesh that’s fully magnetic, so it’s infinitely adjustable for a perfect fit.

fields.name: G-Shock Move
fields.description: Useful workout functions include an optical sensor for heart rate measurement, along with bearing, altitude/barometric pressure, and temperature sensors, and an accelerometer for step counting.

fields.name: 9 Baro
fields.description: Titanium Leather. Ultra-endurance GPS watch with exceptional battery life and barometer, with 2 straps. case dim.

fields.name: Connected
fields.description: Smartwatches powered with Wear OS by Google are compatible with iPhone® and Android™ phones. Wear OS by Google and other related marks are trademarks of Google LLC. Touchscreen smartwatches powered with Wear OS by Google require a phone running Android OS 4.4+ (excluding Go edition) or iOS 10.0+. Supported features may vary between platforms.

fields.name: T-Touch Expert Solar
fields.description: Tissot rounds out our guide with the T-Touch Expert Solar — a premium, high-end model that illustrates the company’s endless pursuit for style and poise.

fields.name: Regulus
fields.description: Manufactured to withstand the most extreme conditions and with a simple design, the Regulus is always ready for action.

fields.name: Prospex SBEP001
fields.description: The Seiko Prospex SBEP001 is a new Fieldmaster watch designed by LOWERCASE. It has a Seiko Caliber S802 solar powered digital quartz movement that features a 5 month power reserve (when fully charged).

fields.name: Seamaster Diver
fields.description:
'Dives' up to 300M 
Co-Axial Master Chronometer

fields.name: DS-8 Chrono Moon Phase
fields.description: An elegant casual watch made by one of the most prestigious watch makers.

fields.name: Racing Horween Leather
fields.description: Skillfully crafted to evoke the nostalgia of 1960s & 1970s speed and motorsport, our Horween Racing Collection pairs perfectly with your watch. The distinguishing perforations, originally designed to create a breathable strap for racetrack drivers, now makes a signature statement on your wrist.

fields.name: Crimson Red Stitching
fields.description: Our Black Leather Quick Release watch bands install in less time than it takes to shake a martini. Crafted from hand-selected top grain leather, this truly is "The Strap Your Watch Deserves."

fields.name: Navy Blue
fields.description:
Navy Blue leather strap with quick change barrette compatible with all 44-46 mm cases.
Handmade in Italy using premium materials.

fields.name: Alligator Grain Leather
fields.description: Our Alligator Grain Leather quick release watch bands feature a 2mm taper from watch head to buckle and are padded for style and comfort. Crafted from hand-selected top grain leather and embossed with premium alligator texture, these straps are sure to be the envy of your town (or at least your break room).

fields.name: Silicone Replacement Strap
fields.description: Navy Blue Elite Silicone - Our Elite Silicone Quick Release navy watch straps feature a premium textured top, a 316L surgical grade brushed stainless steel buckle and a 2mm taper from watch head to buckle. Each navy blue silicone watch band also comes standard with two included lengths to assure they will be a perfect fit for nearly anyone.
